<div class="title">The Sinclair Method</div>
<div class="substance">Naltrexone & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Goin4More&Exact=1">Goin4More</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Goin4More. "The Sinclair Method: An Experience with Naltrexone & Alcohol (exp77806)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 21, 2010. erowid.org/exp/77806</div>

